title: AWS re:Invent 2025 -Go-to-market in today's political climate: a policy and AWS Marketplace overview
title_cn: AWS re:Invent 2025 - 当前政治环境下的市场进入策略：政策与 AWS Marketplace 概述
abstract: Discover how open source projects can transform into profitable businesses through managed services and AI agents, leveraging AWS Global Startup Program support for technical and go-to-market success.
abstract_cn: 了解开源项目如何通过托管服务和AI代理转变为盈利业务,利用AWS全球初创企业计划支持实现技术和市场推广成功。
